l>(Giordana Angi, Antonio Iammarino, Nina Zilli)</small>\n|Valeriano Chiaravalle\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|17\n|\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|\"Il segreto del tempo\" \u2013 [[Pooh (band)|Roby Facchinetti]] & [[Riccardo Fogli]]<br/><small>(Pacifico, Roby Facchinetti)</small>\n|Danilo Ballo\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|18\n|\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|\"Rivederti\" \u2013 [[Mario Biondi]]<br/><small>(Mario Biondi, Giuseppe Furnari, Fisicaro)</small>\n|Peppe Vessicchio\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|19\n|\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|\"Arrivedorci\" \u2013 [[Elio e le Storie Tese]]<br/><small>([[Elio|Stefano Belisari]], Sergio Conforti, Davide Civaschi, Nicola Fasani)</small>\n|Peppe Vessicchio\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|20\n|\n|-\n!colspan=\"4\"|Newcomers' section<ref>{{cite web|url=https://eurovoix.com/2017/12/16/italy-sanremo-2018-participants-announced/|work=Eurovoix|language=EN|accessdate=16 December 2017|title=Italy: Sanremo 2018 Participants Announced|author=Neil Farren|date=16 December 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n! Song, performing artist(s) and writer(s)\n! Orchestra conductor<ref name=\"Orch\" />\n! Rank\n! Sanremo Music Festival Awards\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|\"Il ballo delle incertezze\" \u2013 [[Ultimo (singer)|Ultimo]]<br/><small>(Ultimo)</small>\n|Diego Calvetti\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|1\n|\n* Winner of the Newcomers' section \u2013 Silver Lion<ref name=\"newcomers winner\">{{cite web|url=http://spettacoliecultura.ilmessaggero.it/sanremo/sanremo2018_ultimo_vince_il_premio_per_i_giovani_a_mirkoeilcane_quello_per_la_critica-3538659.html|work=Il Messaggero|language=Italian|accessdate=10 February 2018|title=Sanremo2018, Ultimo vince il premio per i giovani. A Mirkoeilcane quello per la Critica|date=10 February 2018}}</ref>\n* Lunezia Award for Best Music-letterary Value<ref name=\"Lunezia\" />\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|\"Stiamo tutti bene\" \u2013 Mirkoeilcane<br/><small>(Mirkoeilcane)</small>\n|Fio Zanotti\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|2\n|\n* Critics' Award \"Mia Martini\"<ref nam