Bianca\" \u2013 Leonardo Monteiro<br/><small>(Marco Ciappelli, Vladi Tosetto)</small>\n|Dariana Koumanova\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|8\n|\n|-\n|}\n\n==Shows==\n===First evening===\nThe 20 Big Artists each performed their song for the first time.<ref name=\"changes\"/>\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Artist\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Draw\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Song\n! colspan=\"4\" class=\"unsortable\"| Votes\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Place\n|-\n! Public<br/><small>(weight 40%)</small>\n! Demoscopic Jury<br/><small>(weight 30%)</small>\n! Press Jury<br/><small>(weight 30%)</small>\n! Average\n|-\n|[[Annalisa]]\n|1\n|\"Il mondo prima di te\"\n|11th (3.83%)\n|3rd\n|9th\n|4.66%\n|3rd\n|-\n|[[Ron (singer)|Ron]]\n|2\n|\"Almeno pensami\"\n|4th (6.58%)\n|6th\n|6th\n|6.27%\n|4th\n|-\n|[[The Kolors]]\n|3\n|\"Frida\"\n|2nd (10.60%)\n|9th\n|10th\n|6.54%\n|8th\n|-\n|[[Max Gazz\u00e8]]\n|4\n|\"La leggenda di Cristalda e Pizzomunno\"\n|6th (4.61%)\n|5th\n|5th\n|6.26%\n|6th\n|-\n|[[Ornella Vanoni]] feat. Bungaro & [[Pacifico (singer)|Pacifico]]\n|5\n|\"Imparare ad amarsi\"\n|7th (4.39%)\n|8th\n|4th\n|6.268%\n|5th\n|-\n|[[Ermal Meta]] & [[Fabrizio Moro]]\n|6\n|\"[[Non mi avete fatto niente]]\"\n|1st (21.98%)\n|1st\n|2nd\n|16.12%\n|1st\n|-\n|[[Mario Biondi]]\n|7\n|\"Rivederti\"\n|13th (3.45%)\n|11th\n|17th\n|3.19%\n|15th\n|-\n|[[Roby Facchinetti]] & [[Riccardo Fogli]]\n|8\n|\"Il segreto del tempo\"\n|3rd (6.77%)\n|18th\n|19th\n|3.81%\n|11th\n|-\n|[[Lo Stato Sociale]]\n|9\n|\"Una vita in vacanza\"\n|8th (4.27%)\n|2nd\n|1st\n|9.53%\n|2nd\n|-\n|[[Noemi (singer)|Noemi]]\n|10\n|\"Non smettere mai di cercarmi\"\n|14th (3.09%)\n|4th\n|16th\n|3.86%\n|10th\n|-\n|Decibel\n|11\n|\"Fuori dal tempo\"\n|15th (2.81%)\n|15th\n|10th\n|3.10%\n|16th\n|-\n|[[Elio e le Storie Tese]]\n|12\n|\"Arrivedorci\"\n|20th (1.72%)\n|12th\n|18th\n|2.41%\n|20th\n|-\n|[[Giovanni Caccamo]]\n|13\n|\"Eterno\"\n|10th (3.97%)\n|13th\n|12th\n|3.71%\n|12th\n|-\n|[[Red Canzian]]\n|14\n|\"Ognuno ha il suo racconto\"\n|12th (