1-7a8ec16d1e1b.html|title=Il riassunto della serata finale|work=sanremo.rai.it}}</ref>\n|-\n! Press Jury<br/><small>(weight 30%)</small>\n! Expert Jury<br/><small>(weight 20%)</small>\n! Public<br/><small>(weight 50%)</small>\n! Average\n|-bgcolor=#cd7f32\n|[[Annalisa]]\n|1\n|\"[[Il mondo prima di te]]\"\n|3rd \n|1st\n|2nd (23,44%)\n|26,94%\n|3\n|-bgcolor=silver\n|[[Lo Stato Sociale]]\n|2\n|\"[[Una vita in vacanza]]\"\n|1st \n|3rd\n|3rd (22,10%) \n|28,40%\n|2\n|-bgcolor=gold\n|[[Ermal Meta]] & [[Fabrizio Moro]]\n|3\n|\"[[Non mi avete fatto niente]]\"\n|2nd\n|2nd\n|1st (54,41%)\n|44,66%\n|1\n|}\n\n==Special guests==\nThe special guests of Sanremo Music Festival 2018 were:<ref>{{cite web|url=https://eurovoix.com/2018/01/09/italy-italian-dimension-sanremo-2018/|accessdate=10 January 2018|title=Italy: A \u201cMore Italian Dimension\u201d For Sanremo 2018|author=Ewan McCaig|date=9 January 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.vanityfair.it/music/concerti-eventi/2018/01/29/festival-di-sanremo-2018-ospiti-sting-baglioni-morandi-pausini-nannini|accessdate=29 January 2018|title=Sanremo 2018: da Sting a Gianni Morandi, gli ospiti che vedremo|author=Mario Manca|date=29 January 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://movieplayer.it/news/sanremo-2018-gli-ospiti-del-festival-serata-per-serata-big-e-nuove-pro_56359/|accessdate=29 January 2018|title=Gli ospiti di Sanremo 2017, serata per serata!|author=Fabio Fusco|date=5 February 2018}}</ref>\n\n*singers / musicians: [[Biagio Antonacci]], [[Gianni Morandi]], [[Gianna Nannini]], [[Nek]], [[Gino Paoli]],   [[Laura Pausini]], [[Max Pezzali]], [[Piero Pel\u00f9]], [[Danilo Rea]], [[Francesco Renga]], [[Shaggy (musician)|Shaggy]], [[Sting (musician)|Sting]], [[James Taylor]].\n*bands / music groups: [[Il Volo]], [[Negramaro]].\n*actors / comedians / directors / models: [[Stefano Accorsi]], [[Carolina Crescentini]], [[Elena Cucci]], [[Nino Frassica]], [[Rosario Fiorello]], [[Claudia Gerini]], [[Massimo Ghini]], [[Sabrina Impacciatore]], [[Ivano Marescotti]], [[Giulia Michelini]], [[Giampaolo Morelli]], [[Gabriele Muccino]], [[Stefania Sandrelli]], [[Valeria Solarino]], [[Gianmarco Tognazzi]].\n*other notable figures: [[Antonella Clerici]], [[Pippo Baudo]], [[Franca Leosini]], [[Giorgio Panariello]].\n\n==Related shows==\n===Primafestival===\n[[Sergio Assisi]] and [[Melissa Greta Marchetto]] present ''Primafestival'', a small show on air on [[Rai 1]] immediately after [[TG1]]. The show features details, curiosities and news relating to Sanremo Music Festival 2018.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.riviera24.it/2018/01/sergio-assisi-e-melissa-greta-marchetto-condurranno-primafestival-di-sanremo-2018-275771/|work=riviera.it|language=Italian|accessdate=18 January 2018|title=Sergio Assisi e Melissa Greta Marchetto condurranno PrimaFestival di Sanremo 2018.|author=Redazione|date=18 January 2018}}</ref>\n\n===Dopofestival===\n[[Edoardo Leo]] and [[Carolina Di Domenico]], with the participation of [[Sabrina Impacciatore]], [[Rolando Ravello]], [[Paolo Genovese]], [[Rocco Tanica]] and a group of journalists of Italian press, presents ''...tanto siamo tra amici al Dopofestival'', a talk show on air on [[Rai 1]] immediately after Sanremo Music Festival. The show features comments about the Festival as well as interviews to the singers competing in the song contest.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ilfattoquotidiano.it/2018/01/29/sanremo-2018-confermati-i-nomi-dei-conduttori-del-dopofestival-edoardo-leo-e-carolina-di-domenico/4124126/|work=Il Fatto Quotidiano|language=Italian|accessdate=29 January 2018|title=Sanremo 2018, confermati i nomi dei conduttori del Dopofestival: Edoardo Leo e Carolina Di Domenico.|author=Claudia Rosi|date=29 January 2018}}</ref>\n\n==Broadcast and ratings==\n===Local broadcast===\n[[Rai 1]] and [[Rai Radio 2]] are the official broadcasters of the festival in [[Italy]]. The show is also available in streaming via website on [http://www.raiplay.it/ Rai Play].\n\n====Ratings Sanremo Music Festival 2018====\nThe audience is referred to the one of [[Rai 1]].\n\n{|class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center; width:100%;\"\n|-\n!scope=\"col\" style=\"width:8%;\" rowspan=\"2\"|Live Show\n!scope=\"col\" style=\"width:12%;\" rowspan=\"2\"|Timeslot ('''[[Central European Time|UTC+1]]''')\n!scope=\"col\" style=\"width:8%;\" rowspan=\"2\"|Date\n!scope=\"col\" colspan=2|1st time<br><small>(9.00pm - 0.00am)</small>\n!scope=\"col\" colspan=2|2nd time<br><small>(0.00am - 1.00am)</small>\n!scope=\"col\" style=\"width:8%; background:#ffdead;\" colspan=2| Overall audience\n|-\n!scope=\"col\" span style=\"width:10%; font-size:smaller; line-height:100%;\"|Viewers\n!scope=\"col\" span style=\"width:10%; font-size:smaller; line-height:100%;\"|Share (%)\n!scope=\"col\" span style=\"width:10%; font-size:smaller; line-height:100%;\"|Viewers\n!scope=\"col\" span style=\"width:10%; font-size:smaller; line-height:100%;\"|Share (%)\n!scope=\"col\" span style=\"width:10%; font-size:smaller; line-height:100%;\"|Viewers\n!scope=\"col\" span style=\"width:10%; font-size:smaller; line-height:100%;\"|Share (%)\n|-\n!style=\"background:#F9F9F9;text-align:center\"|1st\n|rowspan=\"8\"|<center>9:00 pm</center>\n|February 6<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.davidemaggio.it/archives/158655/ascolti-sanremo-2018-prima-serata-del-6-febbraio-tutti-i-dati|work=davidemaggio.it|language=Italian|accessdate= 7 February 2018|title=Ascolti Sanremo 2018, prima serata del 6 febbraio. Tutti i dati|author=Mattia Buonocore|date=7 February 2018}}</ref>\n|13,776,000\n|51.4%\n|6,624,000\n|55.4%\n|11,603,000\n|52.1%\n|-\n!style=\"background:#F9F9F9;text-align:center\"|2nd\n|February 7<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.davidemaggio.it/archives/158743/ascolti-tv-mercoledi-7-febbraio-2018|language=Italian|accessdate= 8 February 2018|title=Ascolti Sanremo 2018, prima serata del 7 febbraio. Tutti i dati|author=Stefania Stefanelli|date=8 February 2018}}</ref>\n|11,458,000\n|46.6%\n|5,870,000\n|52.9%