o Iervolino\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|3\n|\n* Assomusica Award for Best Stage Presence<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fourzine.it/2018/02/09/sanremo-2018-mudimbi-vince-il-premio-assomusica/|work=Fourzine|language=Italian|accessdate=9 February 2018|title=Sanremo 2018: Mudimbi vince il premio Assomusica|date=9 February 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|\"Il congiuntivo\" \u2013 Lorenzo Baglioni<br/><small>(Lorenzo Baglioni, Michele Baglioni, Lorenzo Piscopo)</small>\n|Diego Calvetti\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|4\n|\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|\"Specchi rotti\" \u2013 Alice Caioli<br/><small>(Alice Caioli, Paolo Muscolino)</small>\n|Massimo Morini\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|5\n|\n* Press, Radio, TV & Web Award \"Lucio Dalla\"<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sanremonews.it/2018/02/10/leggi-notizia/argomenti/festival-di-sanremo/articolo/sanremo2018-alice-caioli-ringrazia-la-sala-stampa-lucio-dalla-per-il-premio-video.html|work=Sanremo News|language=Italian|accessdate=10 February 2018|title=Sanremo2018: Alice Caioli ringrazia la sala stampa \"Lucio Dalla\" per il premio|date=10 February 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|\"Cosa ti salver\u00e0\" \u2013 Eva<br/><small>(Antonio Di Martino, Antonio Filippelli)</small>\n|Clemente Ferrari\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|6\n|\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|\"Come stai\" \u2013 Giulia Casieri<br/><small>(Giulia Casieri, Alfredo Ravasio)</small>\n|Massimo Morini\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|7\n|\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|\"Bianca\" \u2013 Leonardo Monteiro<br/><small>(Marco Ciappelli, Vladi Tosetto)</small>\n|Dariana Koumanova\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|8\n|\n|-\n|}\n\n==Shows==\n===First evening===\nThe 20 Big Artists each performed their song for the first time.<ref name=\"changes\"/>\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Artist\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Draw\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Song\n! colspan=\"4\" class=\"unsortable\"| Votes\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Place\n|-\n! Public<br/><small>(weight 40%)</small>\n! Demoscopic Jury<br/><small>(weight 30%)