iano]] & [[Paolo Rossi]]\n| 6\n| \"Una vita in vacanza\"\n| 3rd (8.77%)\n| 11th\n| 1st\n| 9.01%\n| 2nd\n|-\n| [[Max Gazz\u00e8]] - [[Rita Marcotulli]] & Roberto Gatto\n| 7\n| \"La leggenda di Cristalda e Pizzomunno\"\n| 5th (5.86%)\n| 5th\n| 7th\n| 6.32%\n| 7th\n|-\n| Decibel - [[Midge Ure]]\n| 8\n| \"Lettera dal Duca\"\n| 14th (2.70%)\n| 15th\n| 16th\n| 2.70%\n| 15th\n|-\n| [[Ornella Vanoni]] feat. [[Bungaro]] & [[Pacifico (singer)|Pacifico]] - [[Alessandro Preziosi]]\n| 9\n| \"Imparare ad amarsi\"\n| 8th (4.12%)\n| 3rd\n| 6th\n| 6.61%\n| 5th\n|-\n| [[Diodato]] & [[Roy Paci]] - Ghemon\n| 10\n| \"Adesso\"\n| 13th (2.74%)\n| 5th\n| 2nd\n| 6.44%\n| 6th\n|-\n| [[Roby Facchinetti]] & [[Riccardo Fogli]] - [[Giusy Ferreri]]\n| 11\n| \"Il segreto del tempo\"\n| 11th (3.01%)\n| 15th\n| 19th\n| 2.24%\n| 18th\n|-\n| [[Enzo Avitabile]] & [[Peppe Servillo]] - [[Avion Travel]] & Daby Tour\u00e9\n| 12\n| \"Il coraggio di ogni giorno\"\n| 10th (3.50%)\n| 10th\n| 13th\n| 3.46%\n| 12th\n|-\n| [[Ermal Meta]] & [[Fabrizio Moro]] - [[Simone Cristicchi]]\n| 13\n| \"Non mi avete fatto niente\"\n| 1st (23.71%)\n| 2nd\n| 4th\n| 15.71%\n| 1st\n|-\n| [[Giovanni Caccamo]] - [[Arisa]]\n| 14\n| \"Eterno\"\n| 16th (2.40%)\n| 7th\n| 12th\n| 3.49%\n| 11th\n|-\n| [[Ron (singer)|Ron]] - [[Alice (singer)|Alice]]\n| 15\n| \"Almeno pensami\"\n| 9th (3.58%)\n| 1st\n| 5th\n| 7.00%\n| 4th\n|-\n| [[Red Canzian]] - [[Marco Masini]]\n| 16\n| \"Ognuno ha il suo racconto\"\n| 17th (2.22%)\n| 13th\n| 14th\n| 2.53%\n| 16th\n|-\n| [[The Kolors]] - [[Tullio De Piscopo]] & Enrico Nigiotti\n| 17\n| \"Frida\"\n| 4th (6.62%)\n| 8th\n| 8th\n| 5.65%\n| 8th\n|-\n| [[Luca Barbarossa]] - [[Anna Foglietta]]\n| 18\n| \"Passame er sale\"\n| 6th (5.68%)\n| 3rd\n| 11th\n| 5.46%\n| 9th\n|-\n| [[Nina Zilli]] - [[Sergio Cammariere]]\n| 19\n| \"Senza appartenere\"\n| 19th (1.24%)\n| 14th\n| 17th\n| 2.39%\n| 17th\n|-\n| [[Elio e le storie tese]] - [[Neri per Caso]]\n| 20\n| \"Arrivedorci\"\n| 20th (0.59%)\n| 15th\n| 17th\n| 1.53%\n|